snippet.title: Canabalt Steam gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
http://store.steampowered.com/app/358960

The game that popularized the endless runner genre is finally on Steam with all the new game modes, two-player support, optional 3D graphics and special lyrical cover by Mega Ran!
